description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 49, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 245, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 2 for East, 8 for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10495-72860-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [245 Votes, Top 5% Score]
